    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "`map` is just a fancy way of doing a `merge`\n\n```\nIn [24]: d\nOut[24]: \n  Let  Num\n0   A    1\n1   B    2\n2   C    3\n\nIn [25]: ser\nOut[25]: \nA  1    a\nB  2    b\nC  3    c\nA  4    d\nB  5    e\nC  6    f\ndtype: object\n\nIn [26]: ser.index.names=['Let','Num']\n\nIn [27]: pd.merge(d, ser.reset_index(), on=['Let','Num'])\nOut[27]: \n  Let  Num  0\n0   A    1  a\n1   B    2  b\n2   C    3  c\n```\n"
  },
